      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="40593660">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/103233907/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u103233907-24.jpg" alt="東荷馬" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40593660/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40593660/" class="">第8页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/103233907/" class=" " title="東荷馬">東荷馬</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40593660">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">先生學宗二王，現被尊為新儒學開宗大師。但他並不只重義理，而是兼綜踏實與凌空二義。
據先生所下定義，所謂踏實者，乃「必將論主之經驗與思路，在自家腦蓋演過一番，始能一一得其實解。若只隨文生解，不曾切實理會其來歷，是則泛浮不實，為學大忌。」

腹黑君曰：只可能逼近論主，不可能完全複製論主吧。而吾人之逼近，又乃自以為之逼近。學問難作，良有以矣。

所謂凌空者，乃「擲下書無佛說，無世間種種說，亦無己意可說。其唯..</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-12-06 15:11</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                先生學宗二王，現被尊為新儒學開宗大師。但他並不只重義理，而是兼綜踏實與凌空二義。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>據先生所下定義，所謂踏實者，乃「必將論主之經驗與思路，在自家腦蓋演過一番，始能一一得其實解。若只隨文生解，不曾切實理會其來歷，是則泛浮不實，為學大忌。」<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>腹黑君曰：只可能逼近論主，不可能完全複製論主吧。而吾人之逼近，又乃自以為之逼近。學問難作，良有以矣。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>所謂凌空者，乃「擲下書無佛說，無世間種種說，亦無己意可說。其唯於一切相，都無取著，脫爾神解，機應自然，心無所得，而真理昭然現前。」<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>正能量君曰：這境界好高，尤其凌空一說更是玄之又玄。看起來正是儒道二家的進路。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40593660/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-12-06 15:11
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="28602946">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ching-ting/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="[已注销]" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28602946/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28602946/" class="">第11页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Ching-ting/" class=" " title="[已注销]">[已注销]</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28602946">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">正确之解，诚难得。游心万有而求其理，毋逞空想，毋就成见，毋守偏见，毋视浅见，久之当有正解生。外王之道，不托空言，存乎向往之真，见诸行动实践。实践不力，何能成物？己若未成，何以成物？</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-09-16 22:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>正确之解，诚难得。游心万有而求其理，毋逞空想，毋就成见，毋守偏见，毋视浅见，久之当有正解生。外王之道，不托空言，存乎向往之真，见诸行动实践。实践不力，何能成物？己若未成，何以成物？</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28602946/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-09-16 22:13
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="24977191">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2003488/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg" alt="[已注销]" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24977191/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24977191/" class="">辨伪</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2003488/" class=" " title="[已注销]">[已注销]</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24977191">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">内圣者，深穷宇宙人生根本问题，求得正确解决，正确之解，诚难得。游心万有而求其理，毋逞空想，毋就成见，毋守偏见，毋视浅见，久之当有正解生。
外王之道，不托空言，存乎向往之真，见诸行动实践。实践不力，何能成物？
己若未成，何以成物？故內圣外王，其道一贯，学者宜知。
句句有力。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24977191/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-03-06 14:16</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                内圣者，深穷宇宙人生根本问题，求得正确解决，正确之解，诚难得。游心万有而求其理，毋逞空想，毋就成见，毋守偏见，毋视浅见，久之当有正解生。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>外王之道，不托空言，存乎向往之真，见诸行动实践。实践不力，何能成物？<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>己若未成，何以成物？故內圣外王，其道一贯，学者宜知。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>句句有力。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







